{"tid":1389090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【攪珠遊擊戰】攪珠系統 (公測版 v1.0) 上線喇!!!","createTime":"2019-07-30T21:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T11:00:46.000Z","uid":259321,"like":293,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"ecaa4d858a9cc1d9e3a9cd1a14169b90b960d59f","tid":1389090,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:49:34.000Z","msg":"事沿訓前諗到條橋 (必讀!!!) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是決定搞掂埋個<span style=\"color: red;\">攪珠系統</span>佢!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>【攪珠遊擊戰】攪珠系統 <br />\n(公測版 v1.0) 上線喇!!!</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">步驟①：攪珠當日下午18:00到天文台網頁 <a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/indexc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findexc.htm&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=21e74182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/indexc.htm</a><br />\n查看18:00時 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>沙田, 上水, 屯門, 元朗公園, 赤鱲角, <br />\n香港公園 </strong></span> 和 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天文台</span></strong> 的分區氣溫。<br />\n(請確認為下午6時正的數據, 並cap圖留底)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qc1N7b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQc1N7b1.jpg&h=e6ec03a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">步驟②：攪珠結果用以下方法計算。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Po9HbDV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPo9HbDV.jpg&h=7b18f816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">步驟③：查看得獎警署。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnbuA5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnbuA5E.jpg&h=6857cc30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今期攪珠結果為101，換言之中獎警署為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沙田警署</span></span></strong>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">步驟④：收工，準備賀禮，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全世界去得獎警署賀一賀佢。</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n </div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">跪求各位巴絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1) check下攪珠系統有冇嚴重錯漏<br />\n2) 擇個吉日做我地第一日嘅攪珠遊擊戰嘅揭幕禮</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申1：『攪珠遊擊戰』名稱由絲打leChronique提供!<br />\n利申2 ：用天文台數據嘅概念由201700958巴打提供!<br />\n利申3：警署順序經過連續洗牌5次得出  (洗牌用左<a href=\"https://www.random.org/lists/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.random.org%2Flists%2F&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=38853d73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.random.org/lists/</a>)<br />\n利申4：各警署得獎機率方面不盡完美，為求計算簡單易明，敬請見諒!<br />\n利申5：偏遠地區及缺乏地區支援嘅警署已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d8bfa18c579ecf801bd7d9841accfd65a2e1420","tid":1389090,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d5aedbc846aafe9b793ee084d67dc96acf31d97","tid":1389090,"uid":259321,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:53:10.000Z","msg":"為香港未來<br />\n狗竇轉轉盤<br />\n每日開盤!!!"},{"pid":"a61f6d7178799e4e4cc767fcf3b479ad5eeca184","tid":1389090,"uid":259675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:53:16.000Z","msg":"仲好過嗰個轉轉盤 <img src=\"