sg":"推<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"9faf9c2c4fab488a8171f06a38fc36a45f9d0e86","tid":1389090,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73da989a717e073e82ee3ea10c8c62358a08cb6b","tid":1389090,"uid":217413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0e13b189f075d294799545d0f022c2cfb97075","tid":1389090,"uid":5623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413e365e1c261d6625680c6f72a93804778cd1fb","tid":1389090,"uid":261445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c592a0399191c6dbd7080a3aa0fe2810f3fc74","tid":1389090,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb459ab997427003f28ad6dad699222e2a82ca4","tid":1389090,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"兩千年前孫武用既疲兵戰略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387842</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n親愛的前線，首先真係無言感激你哋嘅付出！<br />\n我想提小小建議，游擊戰 和理非人都可以有參與機會<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<br />\n1 求下你哋，日日黑衫full gear番工番學同行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線已經犧牲咗咁多，我哋又唔敢上前線，拜託大家幫幫手，唔好淨係識去行下，行完番歸睇直播啦！<br />\nFull gear出街對前線幫助真係好撚大，起碼唔洗發完夢就掉gear。gear短缺，千金難買啊！捐錢備佢哋食飯，不如買gear自己著出街。又唔犯法，抄牌咪抄囉，你又唔會上前線，怕咩備人抄！<br />\n<br />\n2 幫手游擊戰，戰略：<br />\n如果目測，咦！而條街有好多黑衣人喎，550up先好做。<br />\n暗號：（光復香港，時代革命！）<br />\n聽到有人叫，我哋即和應，然後搵一條最近嘅紅綠燈，由綠燈坐到紅燈，直至犬黎。一見到犬，頭也不回，即作鳥獸散。 <br />\n而個可能需要同哨小隊商討到時點睇水。<br />\n遍地開花，撚死狗！<br />\n<br />\n前線巴打：<br />\n和理非啲死人性格，一定唔會主動出擊。<br />\n1 麻煩你哋到時清清喉嚨，幫手大叫暗號，同埋叫人出去一齊過馬路<br />\n<br />\n2 如果有犬，你哋對開防暴犬，催淚彈食到厭，槍聲聽到免疫，相信啲藍衫犬對你哋黎講小case，唔撚識驚。但和理非見到藍衫犬，一撚定好驚。麻煩到時幫手疏散和理非，定一定佢哋小鹿亂撞嘅心。 <br />\n<br />\n親愛的前線，如果冇目標，就唔好再守啦。<br />\n612 第一次正式大型警民衝突<br />\n71 垃圾會<br />\n721 愛國愛黨徽<br />\n呢啲有目標，正！<br />\n728 見到真係有樽頸位，又折損咁多手足，好撚心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊幫手打游擊好唔好？一黎真係好溫和，唔會有暴力場面備cctvb影到，二黎成本低，就算捉到，我相信點都唔會判到有罪！"},{"pid":"dd124532bea5e086f9924a12193ef9407bd14465","tid":1389090,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f83fee51002b0da76d6602695b5d5939c006544","tid":1389090,"uid":17376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"個Range咁大差距<br />\n葵涌0-8咪永遠唔使去？"},{"pid":"f1b110297deffd90c050bf2ae8e98a3f29fb651c","tid":1389090,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"好緊張啊"},{"pid":"35ad1a74f46e51757d9256fec4b15ac1ca3e116d","tid":1389090,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7d034e3b48c69b12b6f74744747ffa346834722","tid":1389090,"uid":259321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f83fee51002b0da76d6602695b5d5939c006544","tid":1389090,"uid":17376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"個Range咁大差距<br />\n葵涌0-8咪永遠唔使去？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"所以取個位和小數後一位<br />\n理論上已經好隨機<br />\n如果溫度總和的個位和小數後一位約 0.0-0.2<br /